Package it.polimi.ingsw.shared.view.remote

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RMIMessageProxy
    Interface that represents the remote object used as proxy between the client and the server to exchange messages
    RMIStreamProvider
    Interface that represents the end point provided by the server to the clients that want to join the game
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InputStreamMessageSupplier
    An input message supplier that waits for data to be available into a given input stream, parses it and then return a Message instance
    MessageDispatcher
    This class asynchronously dispatches the messages from the input and output queues provided a supplier and a consumer for those messages
    OutputStreamMessageConsumer
    Message consumer based on output streams.
